---
import Button from "../primitives/Button.astro"; import Eyebrow from "../primitives/Eyebrow.astro"; import Icon from "../primitives/Icon.astro"; import { consultationFormats } from "../../data/experiencePages";
---
<section class="consultation" aria-labelledby="consultation-heading"><header><Eyebrow>Designer Consultation</Eyebrow><h1 id="consultation-heading">A private conversation before the first sketch</h1><p>Choose how you would like to meet the Rangbastra team. Availability is confirmed personally after your request—this preview does not imply live calendar inventory.</p></header><div class="formats">{consultationFormats.map(format=><article><Icon name={format.icon} size={24}/><h2>{format.title}</h2><p>{format.detail}</p><small>{format.response}</small><Button href={`/design-your-outfit?consultation=${format.id}`}>Request This Format</Button></article>)}</div><div class="consultation-grid"><section><Eyebrow>Calendar Preview</Eyebrow><h2>Appointments are confirmed personally</h2><p>Share your preferred days and time window in the detailed request. The team replies with the closest available appointment.</p><div class="calendar" aria-label="Illustrative appointment sequence"><span>01 · Request</span><span>02 · Availability reply</span><span>03 · Confirmed appointment</span></div></section><section><Eyebrow>Prepare</Eyebrow><h2>Bring what helps us understand you</h2><ul><li>Celebration date and location</li><li>Preferred silhouettes and comfort needs</li><li>Inspiration images or saved Rangbastra pieces</li><li>Budget range and delivery timeline</li><li>Existing measurements, if available</li></ul></section></div><section class="after"><Eyebrow>After Booking</Eyebrow><ol><li><strong>Context review</strong><span>Your selected product, saved inspiration and submitted details are reviewed.</span></li><li><strong>Private conversation</strong><span>The designer discusses direction, feasibility and next decisions.</span></li><li><strong>Detailed brief</strong><span>You continue to the final request only when the direction feels right.</span></li></ol></section></section>
<style>
  .consultation{display:grid;gap:clamp(var(--space-8),9vw,var(--space-12));padding-top:clamp(var(--space-12),14vw,var(--space-14))}.consultation header{display:grid;max-width:60rem;gap:var(--space-5)}h1,h2{color:var(--text-primary);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--weight-light);line-height:1}h1{max-width:14ch;font-size:clamp(3.2rem,7vw,7.8rem)}h2{font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3.8rem)}p,li,small{color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:var(--leading-body)}.formats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:var(--space-4)}article,.consultation-grid>section,.after{display:grid;gap:var(--space-4);padding:clamp(var(--space-5),4vw,var(--space-7));border:1px solid var(--cocoa-border-soft);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);background:#030303;justify-items:start}.consultation-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:var(--space-5)}.calendar{display:grid;width:100%;gap:var(--space-2)}.calendar span,.after li{padding:var(--space-3);border-left:2px solid rgba(var(--cocoa-rgb),.55);background:rgba(var(--cocoa-rgb),.06)}ul,ol{display:grid;gap:var(--space-3);padding-left:1.2rem}.after ol{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));padding:0;list-style:none}.after li{display:grid;gap:var(--space-2)}.after strong{color:var(--text-primary)}@media(max-width:850px){.formats,.consultation-grid,.after ol{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
